{"tid":985110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣清晨實彈演習　模擬解放軍登陸","createTime":"2019-01-17T10:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T07:55:47.000Z","uid":75969,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"64ff3fdd661eb401048164ff755de2743f86b685","tid":985110,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190117/s00004/8e4313a6e11f676567a77909758dd047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190117%2Fs00004%2F8e4313a6e11f676567a77909758dd047.jpg&h=c19b1d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190117/s00004/8e4626be9376b134e4a12bf5c3795267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190117%2Fs00004%2F8e4626be9376b134e4a12bf5c3795267.jpg&h=dc0e6d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣國防部今日清晨5時在台中清水的甲南海灘，舉行「聯合反登陸作戰」實彈演習，以及「反擊部隊再戰整備」實兵演練，模擬大陸解放軍集結登陸，進攻台灣中部地區，國防部需反擊的情况。其間出動的陸空兵力，包括雷霆2000多管火箭、重砲和雲豹裝甲車等。<br />\n<br />\n舉行演練的第五作戰區表示，演練項目包括「聯合火力、舟波攻擊及灘岸火殲暨反擊作戰」等，由於相信甲南海灘是解放軍登陸的主要區域，選址當地可驗證作戰計畫，讓軍人熟悉環境。<br />\n<br />\n第五作戰區另指出，今次演練可展示火力及戰力，亦可充分彰顯軍隊戰備訓練的具體成果，和執行聯合作戰指揮等能力。<br />\n<br />\n（聯合新聞網/中時電子報/中國廣播公司）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190117/s00004/1547715525633/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190117%2Fs00004%2F1547715525633%2F&d=3m4rN%2F1AIvPT8ELKuhEPHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=bad249d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190117%2Fs00004%2F1547715525633%2F&h=dbea0832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190117/s00004/1547715525633/</a>"},{"pid":"8e20af6c40ed7bdefe6bed7ffce319362e811876","tid":985110,"uid":1779,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"離題小小講 今時今日有徵兵制既國